---
import BaseLayout from '@layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="Wood Mantels + Surrounds | Heat & Glo Accessories" description="Heat & Glo wood mantels: hardwood mantel and surround profiles in traditional, transitional, and contemporary styles, engineered to pair with the fireplace lineup." noIndex={true}>
  <main class="max-w-page mx-auto px-4 py-12">
    <header class="mb-12">
      <p class="uppercase tracking-wide text-sm text-orange-700 font-semibold">Wood Mantels</p>
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mt-2">Wood mantels in profiles that pair.</h1>
      <p class="mt-4 text-lg text-neutral-700 max-w-2xl">Hardwood mantel and surround profiles in traditional corbeled, transitional, and contemporary linear styles. Heat & Glo wood mantel collections are engineered to compatible clearance specs for every fireplace family.</p>
    </header>
    <section class="bg-neutral-50 rounded-lg p-6 mb-16"><p class="text-sm text-neutral-700">Wood mantel product detail pages populate from the HHT accessory catalog as the rebuild scales beyond the pitch deliverable. Confirm clearance-to-combustibles requirements with the installation manual before specifying any wood mantel.</p></section>
    <p class="text-neutral-600 border-t pt-10"><a href="/accessories/" class="underline">Back to all accessories</a></p>
  </main>
</BaseLayout>
